      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEAR ME ROAR (8) scored two back when on speed but last start drifted back and could manage only a 6 length 4th at this track (19.65). Key runner on his best form. ALL ON BARNEY (1) well back settling but did wind up strongly to finish 4th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (18.39) at Richmond. Maiden this journey but has some solid runs behind him. Cannot be left out. WESTBURN HARADA (7) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing third (19.80) at this track in a Grade 5 over 340m. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Leading chance. SIDE SHOW BOB (2) is a last start winner who can measure up again.",
